https://github.com/ali1234/piroverd

Implements a Wi-Fi first-person-video vehicle. Video is captured from
the rpi camera, encoded to h264 by the GPU, and streamed over rtsp
by gstreamer. Control input is received over UDP.

Hardware used:

 - Raspberry Pi Model A+
 - Raspberry Pi Camera
 - Adafruit DC motor hat (PCA9685)
 - Sparkfun lipo fuel gauge (MAX17043)
 - Pimoroni 18 Channel LED driver (SN3218)
 - Ebay Special MPU9150 9DOF motion sensor (MPU6050+AK8975)

Full construction details to be released later...

Dependencies:

 - gst-rpicamsrc (https://github.com/thaytan/gst-rpicamsrc)
 - gstrtspserver-1.0
 - gstreamer-1.0
 - gio-2.0
 - glib-2.0
